      "review_summary": "The PR adds gateway discovery of `{session}.checkpoint.<uuid>.jsonl` files from disk for session-list previews and `sessions.compaction.list/get/branch/restore` when persisted checkpoint metadata is missing.\n\nPR surface: Source +500, Tests +697. Total +1197 across 7 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level reproduction is high confidence: current main only reads stored checkpoint metadata while the linked report and PR proof cover valid checkpoint files existing on disk without `compactionCheckpoints` metadata.",
